data.description: Seller now offering $1000 use as you choose credit as well as a one year home warranty with purchase! No HOA & no city taxes! Ready for move in! Conveniently located just outside city limits in Midway Park, this home is just 5 minutes to access the main gates of Camp Lejeune and only  10 minutes to the center of Jacksonville, NC. 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, split floorplan with the master bedroom opposite of the other two bedrooms. When you first walk in you'll be greeted with a large living room area attached to a separate formal dining room or additional living area with fireplace. Into the kitchen area where the cabinets are painted grey with all black appliances and a separate pantry. Outside you have a fully fenced backyard, covered porch, and shed for all your outdoor needs. No HOA & no city taxes! Call to schedule a tour today!
